document.full_text: eman al-obeidy, a libyan woman who said that she was gang-raped by members of col. muammar el-qaddafi's security forces in march, was expelled from qatar on thursday, and arrived in libya with bruises and scars.
document.title: the lede: libyan dissident says she was beaten in qatar
